title: Presidential candidate Bush raises $13.4 million in latest quarter
text: WASHINGTON (Reuters) - Jeb Bush, who has struggled to connect with voters in his bid for the Republican presidential nomination, reported raising $13.4 million in the latest quarter on Thursday, an amount that pales in comparison to the heady, early days of his campaign.
